{"title_page": "Puerto Rico Highway 145", "text_new": "{{short description|Highway in Puerto Rico}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=August 2019}}\n[[File:Puerto Rico Highway 145 in Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico.jpg|thumb|right|290px|Puerto Rico Highway 145 in Torrecillas, a barrio of Morovis]]\n{{Infobox road\n|state=PR\n|type=PR\n|route=145\n|alternate_name=\n|maint=[[Puerto Rico Department of Transportation and Public Works|Puerto Rico DTPW]]\n|length_km=7.5\n|length_ref=<ref name=google/>\n|direction_a=West\n|terminus_a={{Jct|state=PR|Sec|146|Sec|149}} in [[Jaguas, Ciales, Puerto Rico|Jaguas]]\n|junction={{plainlist|1=\n*{{Jct|state=PR|Sec|6632}} in Jaguas\n*{{Jct|state=PR|Ter|567|Ter|6622}} in [[Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Torrecillas]]\u2013[[Morovis Norte]]\n}}\n|direction_b=East\n|terminus_b={{Jct|state=PR|Sec|155|Ter|634}} in Morovis Norte\u2013Torrecillas\u2013[[Fr\u00e1nquez, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Fr\u00e1nquez]]\n|municipalities=[[Ciales, Puerto Rico|Ciales]], [[Morovis, Puerto Rico|Morovis]]\n|previous_type=Sec\n|previous_route=144\n|next_type=Sec\n|next_route=146\n}}\n'''Puerto Rico Highway 145''' ('''PR-145''') is a rural road that travels from [[Ciales, Puerto Rico]] to [[Morovis, Puerto Rico|Morovis]].<ref name=\"NGAdvMap\">{{cite map |author = National Geographic Maps |year = 2011 |title = Puerto Rico |series = Adventure Map |scale = 1:125,000 |location = Evergreen, CO |publisher = National Geographic Maps |sections = |isbn=978-1566955188 |oclc = 756511572 }}</ref> This road extends from its junction with [[Puerto Rico Highway 145|PR-145]] and [[Puerto Rico Highway 149|PR-149]] in downtown Ciales and ends at [[Puerto Rico Highway 155|PR-155]] between [[Morovis Norte]], [[Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Torrecillas]] and [[Fr\u00e1nquez, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Fr\u00e1nquez]] ''barrios''.<ref name=\"DTOP Transit Data\">{{cite web |title = Tr\u00e1nsito Promedio Diario (AADT) |url = http://act.dtop.pr.gov/index.php/download/traffic-data-report-2000-2009/?wpdmdl=528 |website = [[Puerto Rico Department of Transportation and Public Works]] |page = 79 |language = spanish |accessdate = May 30, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Major intersections==\n{{PRinttop|length_ref=<ref name=google>{{google maps|url=https://www.google.com/maps/dir/18.3420947,-66.4676959/18.3362396,-66.4270618/@18.3333576,-66.4561336,15z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m9!4m8!1m5!3m4!1m2!1d-66.4486754!2d18.3257188!3s0x8c03235d40a4175b:0x5ecad8067433262b!1m0!3e0|title=PR-145|accessdate=March 2, 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{PRint\n|municipality=Ciales\n|munspan=2\n|location=Jaguas\n|ctdab=Ciales\n|lspan=2\n|km=0.0\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|146|dir1=west|Sec|149|city1=Ciales|city2=Manat\u00ed|city3=Utuado}}\n|notes=Western terminus of PR-145\n}}\n{{PRint\n|km=0.7\n|km2=0.8\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|6632|dir1=south|city1=Jayuya|city2=Villalba}}\n|notes=\n}}\n{{PRint\n|municipality=Morovis\n|munspan=2\n|location1=Torrecillas\n|location2=Morovis Norte\n|km=6.6\n|km2=6.7\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Ter|567|Ter|6622|name2=Carretera Licenciado H\u00e9ctor \"Chiqui\" Russe Mart\u00ednez|city1=Morovis}}\n|notes=\n}}\n{{PRint\n|location1=Morovis Norte\n|location2=Torrecillas\n|location3=Fr\u00e1nquez\n|km=7.5\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|155|Ter|634|city1=Morovis|city2=Vega Baja}}\n|notes=Eastern terminus of PR-145\n}}\n{{jctbtm}}\n\n==See also==\n{{stack|{{portal|Puerto Rico|U.S. Roads}}}}\n*[[List of highways in Puerto Rico]]\n*[[List of highways numbered 145]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|22em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category-inline|Puerto Rico Highway 145}}\n\n[[Category:Highways in Puerto Rico|145]]\n\n\n{{PuertoRico-road-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Highway in Puerto Rico}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=August 2019}}\n[[File:Puerto Rico Highway 145 in Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico.jpg|thumb|right|290px|Puerto Rico Highway 145 in Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico]]\n{{Infobox road\n|state=PR\n|type=PR\n|route=145\n|alternate_name=\n|maint=[[Puerto Rico Department of Transportation and Public Works|Puerto Rico DTPW]]\n|length_km=7.5\n|length_ref=<ref name=google/>\n|direction_a=West\n|terminus_a={{Jct|state=PR|Sec|146|Sec|149}} in [[Jaguas, Ciales, Puerto Rico|Jaguas]]\n|junction={{plainlist|1=\n*{{Jct|state=PR|Sec|6632}} in Jaguas\n*{{Jct|state=PR|Ter|567|Ter|6622}} in [[Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Torrecillas]]\u2013[[Morovis Norte]]\n}}\n|direction_b=East\n|terminus_b={{Jct|state=PR|Sec|155|Ter|634}} in Morovis Norte\u2013Torrecillas\u2013[[Fr\u00e1nquez, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Fr\u00e1nquez]]\n|municipalities=[[Ciales, Puerto Rico|Ciales]], [[Morovis, Puerto Rico|Morovis]]\n|previous_type=Sec\n|previous_route=144\n|next_type=Sec\n|next_route=146\n}}\n'''Puerto Rico Highway 145''' ('''PR-145''') is a rural road that travels from [[Ciales, Puerto Rico]] to [[Morovis, Puerto Rico|Morovis]].<ref name=\"NGAdvMap\">{{cite map |author = National Geographic Maps |year = 2011 |title = Puerto Rico |series = Adventure Map |scale = 1:125,000 |location = Evergreen, CO |publisher = National Geographic Maps |sections = |isbn=978-1566955188 |oclc = 756511572 }}</ref> This road extends from its junction with [[Puerto Rico Highway 145|PR-145]] and [[Puerto Rico Highway 149|PR-149]] in downtown Ciales and ends at [[Puerto Rico Highway 155|PR-155]] between [[Morovis Norte]], [[Torrecillas, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Torrecillas]] and [[Fr\u00e1nquez, Morovis, Puerto Rico|Fr\u00e1nquez]] ''barrios''.<ref name=\"DTOP Transit Data\">{{cite web |title = Tr\u00e1nsito Promedio Diario (AADT) |url = http://act.dtop.pr.gov/index.php/download/traffic-data-report-2000-2009/?wpdmdl=528 |website = [[Puerto Rico Department of Transportation and Public Works]] |page = 79 |language = spanish |accessdate = May 30, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Major intersections==\n{{PRinttop|length_ref=<ref name=google>{{google maps|url=https://www.google.com/maps/dir/18.3420947,-66.4676959/18.3362396,-66.4270618/@18.3333576,-66.4561336,15z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m9!4m8!1m5!3m4!1m2!1d-66.4486754!2d18.3257188!3s0x8c03235d40a4175b:0x5ecad8067433262b!1m0!3e0|title=PR-145|accessdate=March 2, 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{PRint\n|municipality=Ciales\n|munspan=2\n|location=Jaguas\n|ctdab=Ciales\n|lspan=2\n|km=0.0\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|146|dir1=west|Sec|149|city1=Ciales|city2=Manat\u00ed|city3=Utuado}}\n|notes=Western terminus of PR-145\n}}\n{{PRint\n|km=0.7\n|km2=0.8\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|6632|dir1=south|city1=Jayuya|city2=Villalba}}\n|notes=\n}}\n{{PRint\n|municipality=Morovis\n|munspan=2\n|location1=Torrecillas\n|location2=Morovis Norte\n|km=6.6\n|km2=6.7\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Ter|567|Ter|6622|name2=Carretera Licenciado H\u00e9ctor \"Chiqui\" Russe Mart\u00ednez|city1=Morovis}}\n|notes=\n}}\n{{PRint\n|location1=Morovis Norte\n|location2=Torrecillas\n|location3=Fr\u00e1nquez\n|km=7.5\n|road={{jct|state=PR|Sec|155|Ter|634|city1=Morovis|city2=Vega Baja}}\n|notes=Eastern terminus of PR-145\n}}\n{{jctbtm}}\n\n==See also==\n{{stack|{{portal|Puerto Rico|U.S. Roads}}}}\n*[[List of highways in Puerto Rico]]\n*[[List of highways numbered 145]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|22em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category-inline|Puerto Rico Highway 145}}\n\n[[Category:Highways in Puerto Rico|145]]\n\n\n{{PuertoRico-road-stub}}\n", "name_user": "The Eloquent Peasant", "label": "safe", "comment": "minor change to caption", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puerto_Rico_Highway_145"}
{"title_page": "Reyko", "text_new": "{{Infobox musical artist\n| name            = REYKO\n| background      = group_or_band\n| image           = REYKO at Sala El Sol, Madrid in 2019.jpg\n| image_size      = 250\n| landscape       = yes\n| caption         = REYKO at Sala El Sol, [[Madrid]] in 2019\n| origin          = [[London]]\n| genre           = {{flatlist| \n* [[electropop]]\n* [[synthpop]]\n* [[dancepop]]\n* [[indiepop]]\n}}\n| years_active    = 2015\u2013present\n| label           = {{flatlist|\n* \n* REYKO\n* [[Warner Music]]\n* [[Universal Music]]\n* Mushroom Pillow\n}}\n| website         = {{URL|http://reykomusic.com}}\n| current_members = Soleil<br/>Igor\n}}\n\n'''Reyko''' (stylized \"REYKO\") are a London-based [[electropop]] duo, consisting of vocalist Soleil and producer and multi instrumentalist Igor.\n\n==History==\nThe two members of Reyko, Soleil and Igor, are from [[Spain]] but are currently based in [[London]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Reyko, autores de \"Spinning Over You\", vuelven con dos nuevos sencillos |url=https://www.efe.com/efe/espana/cultura/reyko-autores-de-spinning-over-you-vuelven-con-dos-nuevos-sencillos/10005-4065867 |agency=[[EFE]] |date=September 17, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref name=van>{{cite news |title=El grupo espa\u00f1ol REYKO debuta con su primer disco el pr\u00f3ximo 6 de marzo |url=https://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20200228/473825610897/el-grupo-espanol-reyko-debuta-con-su-primer-disco-el-proximo-6-de-marzo.html |work=[[La Vanguardia]] |agency=[[EFE]] |date=February 28, 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref> Before forming the duo, Soleil worked as an osteopath, and Igor was a professional tennis player before deciding to pursue a music career.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Palao Murcia |first1=Alberto |title=Reyko: \"Tenemos en mente desde hace tiempo hacer una mezcla entre espa\u00f1ol e ingl\u00e9s\" |date=15 March 2018 |url=https://los40.com/los40/2018/03/15/musica/1521133907_129835.html |publisher=[[Los 40]] |accessdate=March 23, 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Hernandez Velasco |first1=Irene |title=Reyko: \"Hacemos m\u00fasica para desconectar de la pol\u00edtica\" |url=https://www.elmundo.es/papel/historias/2018/09/15/5b9bab82268e3ed84b8b457f.html |work=[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]] |date=September 15, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref> They started writing music together as part of Igor's music production course.<ref>{{cite web |title=Reyko lanza \"Hierba mala\" |url=https://www.cadena100.es/al-dia/noticias/reyko-lanza-hierba-mala-20180830_323682 |publisher=[[:es:Cadena 100|Cadena 100]] |date=August 30, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\nThe duo's debut single, \"Spinning Over You\", was the official song for a major 2018 ad campaign by [[El Corte Ingles]] and became a radio hit in [[Spain]], peaking at #13 nationally.<ref>{{cite news |title=La canci\u00f3n del anuncio de El Corte Ingl\u00e9s para las rebajas de verano 2018 |url=https://www.lasprovincias.es/culturas/musica/cancion-anuncio-corte-ingles-verano-20180630131123-nt.html |work=[[Las Provincias]] |date=June 30, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Spain Singles Top 50|url=https://acharts.co/spain_singles_top_50/2018/02 |website=Acharts.co ([[Promusicae]])|date=January 14, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Ferrero |first1=Clara |title=Reyko, el d\u00fao espa\u00f1ol de electr\u00f3nica pop que se hizo viral en todo el mundo |url=https://smoda.elpais.com/placeres/reyko-duo-espanol-electronica-pop/ |work=[[El Pa\u00eds]] |date=July 12, 2017}}</ref> In 2018, Reyko were nominated for best new artist in [[LOS40 Music Awards 2018|LOS40 Music Awards]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Los 40 Music Awards 2018: artistas nominados |url=https://los40.com/especiales/los40-music-awards/2018/nominados/ |publisher=[[Los 40]] |accessdate=26 October 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn April 2019, Reyko contributed a version of \"El Cine\" to a [[Warner Music]] tribute album consisting of covers to [[Mecano]]'s album ''[[Descanso Dominical]]''.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sarria |first1=Belen |title=Doble homenaje a 'Descanso Dominical', el disco que consagr\u00f3 a Mecano |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/3629978/0/doble-homenaje-descanso-dominical-disco-consagro-mecano/ |work=[[20 minutos]] |issue=May 3, 2019 |language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\nIn mid 2019, the duo decided to break ties with their then label Mushroom Pillow and self release their future music, after they found out the label was licensing their unreleased music without their knowledge. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://los40.com/los40/2019/08/23/videoclips/1566394193_968264.html|title=REYKO - Lose Myself [2019]|last=LOS40|date=2019-08-21|website=LOS40|language=es|access-date=2020-04-17}}</ref> \n\n\nBetween August 2019 and January 2020, the duo released a series of singles: \"Lose Myself\", followed by \"Hierba Mala\", \"Don't Mention My Name\", \"Surrender\" and \"La Verdad\".<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moral |first1=Selene |title=Justin Bieber, David Bisbal y Ava Max: Escucha las primeras canciones de 2020 |url=https://los40.com/los40/2020/01/03/musica/1578045910_737383.html |publisher=[[Los 40]] |date=January 3, 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Murray |first1=Robin |title=REYKO raise the temperature with lose myself |url=https://www.clashmusic.com/news/reyko-raise-the-temperature-with-lose-myself |website=[[Clash Music]] |accessdate=27 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Villacanas |first1=Javier |title=REYKO estrena nueva canci\u00f3n: \"Don't Mention My Name\" como antesala de su \u00e1lbum debut |url=https://www.cadena100.es/musica/noticias/reyko-estrena-nueva-cancion-dont-mention-name-20191025_535748 |publisher=[[Los 40]] |date=October 25, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Moreno |first1=Violeta |title=Reyko, el dueto espa\u00f1ol cuya m\u00fasica sale en 'La casa de las flores' |url=https://www.milenio.com/espectaculos/musica/reyko-dueto-espanol-aparece-casa-flores |website=[[Milenio]] |date=October 28, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref> In March 2020, the duo released their self-titled debut album, which includes their previously released singles.<ref name=\"van\" />  \n\n\"Set You Free\", which appears on their EP ''Midnight Sunshine'', is the theme song for the [[Netflix]] series ''Toy Boy''.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moreno |first1=Adriano |title=Los secretos que esconde 'Set You Free', la sensual sintonia de 'Toy Boy' |url=https://los40.com/los40/2019/09/25/musica/1569410777_628986.html |publisher=[[Los 40]]|language=Spanish|date=September 25, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n=== Studio albums ===\n* ''REYKO'' (2020)\n\n===EPs===\n*''Midnight Sunshine'' (2018)\n\n=== Singles ===\n* \"Spinning Over You\" (2017)\n* \"Lose Myself\" (2019) \n* \"Hierba Mala\" (2019) \n* \"Don't Mention my Name\" (2019)\n* \"Surrender\" (2020)\n* \"La Verdad\" (2020)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.reykomusic.com Official website]\n\n\n\n[[Category:Electropop groups]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox musical artist\n| name            = REYKO\n| background      = group_or_band\n| image           = REYKO at Sala El Sol, Madrid in 2019.jpg\n| image_size      = 250\n| landscape       = yes\n| caption         = REYKO at Sala El Sol, [[Madrid]] in 2019\n| origin          = [[London]]\n| genre           = {{flatlist| \n* [[electropop]]\n* [[synthpop]]\n* [[dancepop]]\n* [[indiepop]]\n}}\n| years_active    = 2015\u2013present\n| label           = {{flatlist|\n* \n* REYKO\n* [[Warner Music]]\n* [[Universal Music]]\n* Mushroom Pillow\n}}\n| website         = {{URL|http://reykomusic.com}}\n| current_members = Soleil<br/>Igor\n}}\n\n'''Reyko''' (stylized \"REYKO\") are a London-based [[electropop]] duo, consisting of vocalist Soleil and producer and multi instrumentalist Igor.\n\n==History==\nThe two members of Reyko, Soleil and Igor, are from [[Spain]] but are currently based in [[London]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Reyko, autores de \"Spinning Over You\", vuelven con dos nuevos sencillos |url=https://www.efe.com/efe/espana/cultura/reyko-autores-de-spinning-over-you-vuelven-con-dos-nuevos-sencillos/10005-4065867 |agency=[[EFE]] |date=September 17, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref name=van>{{cite news |title=El grupo espa\u00f1ol REYKO debuta con su primer disco el pr\u00f3ximo 6 de marzo |url=https://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20200228/473825610897/el-grupo-espanol-reyko-debuta-con-su-primer-disco-el-proximo-6-de-marzo.html |work=[[La Vanguardia]] |agency=[[EFE]] |date=February 28, 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref> Before forming Reyko, Soleil worked as an osteopath, and Igor was a professional tennis player before deciding to pursue a music career.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Palao Murcia |first1=Alberto |title=Reyko: \"Tenemos en mente desde hace tiempo hacer una mezcla entre espa\u00f1ol e ingl\u00e9s\" |date=15 March 2018 |url=https://los40.com/los40/2018/03/15/musica/1521133907_129835.html |publisher=[[Los 40]] |accessdate=March 23, 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Hernandez Velasco |first1=Irene |title=Reyko: \"Hacemos m\u00fasica para desconectar de la pol\u00edtica\" |url=https://www.elmundo.es/papel/historias/2018/09/15/5b9bab82268e3ed84b8b457f.html |work=[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]] |date=September 15, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref> They started writing music together as part of Igor's music production course.<ref>{{cite web |title=Reyko lanza \"Hierba mala\" |url=https://www.cadena100.es/al-dia/noticias/reyko-lanza-hierba-mala-20180830_323682 |publisher=[[:es:Cadena 100|Cadena 100]] |date=August 30, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\nThe duo's debut single, \"Spinning Over You\", was the official song for a major 2018 ad campaign by [[El Corte Ingles]] and became a radio hit in [[Spain]], peaking at #13 nationally.<ref>{{cite news |title=La canci\u00f3n del anuncio de El Corte Ingl\u00e9s para las rebajas de verano 2018 |url=https://www.lasprovincias.es/culturas/musica/cancion-anuncio-corte-ingles-verano-20180630131123-nt.html |work=[[Las Provincias]] |date=June 30, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Spain Singles Top 50|url=https://acharts.co/spain_singles_top_50/2018/02 |website=Acharts.co ([[Promusicae]])|date=January 14, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Ferrero |first1=Clara |title=Reyko, el d\u00fao espa\u00f1ol de electr\u00f3nica pop que se hizo viral en todo el mundo |url=https://smoda.elpais.com/placeres/reyko-duo-espanol-electronica-pop/ |work=[[El Pa\u00eds]] |date=July 12, 2017}}</ref> In 2018, Reyko were nominated for best new artist in [[LOS40 Music Awards 2018|LOS40 Music Awards]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Los 40 Music Awards 2018: artistas nominados |url=https://los40.com/especiales/los40-music-awards/2018/nominados/ |publisher=[[Los 40]] |accessdate=26 October 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn April 2019, Reyko contributed a version of \"El Cine\" to a [[Warner Music]] tribute album consisting of covers to [[Mecano]]'s album ''[[Descanso Dominical]]''.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sarria |first1=Belen |title=Doble homenaje a 'Descanso Dominical', el disco que consagr\u00f3 a Mecano |url=https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/3629978/0/doble-homenaje-descanso-dominical-disco-consagro-mecano/ |work=[[20 minutos]] |issue=May 3, 2019 |language=Spanish}}</ref> \n\nBetween August 2019 and January 2020, the duo released a series of singles: \"Lose Myself\", followed by \"Hierba Mala\", \"Don't Mention My Name\", \"Surrender\" and \"La Verdad\".<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moral |first1=Selene |title=Justin Bieber, David Bisbal y Ava Max: Escucha las primeras canciones de 2020 |url=https://los40.com/los40/2020/01/03/musica/1578045910_737383.html |publisher=[[Los 40]] |date=January 3, 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Murray |first1=Robin |title=REYKO raise the temperature with lose myself |url=https://www.clashmusic.com/news/reyko-raise-the-temperature-with-lose-myself |website=[[Clash Music]] |accessdate=27 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Villacanas |first1=Javier |title=REYKO estrena nueva canci\u00f3n: \"Don't Mention My Name\" como antesala de su \u00e1lbum debut |url=https://www.cadena100.es/musica/noticias/reyko-estrena-nueva-cancion-dont-mention-name-20191025_535748 |publisher=[[Los 40]] |date=October 25, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Moreno |first1=Violeta |title=Reyko, el dueto espa\u00f1ol cuya m\u00fasica sale en 'La casa de las flores' |url=https://www.milenio.com/espectaculos/musica/reyko-dueto-espanol-aparece-casa-flores |website=[[Milenio]] |date=October 28, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref> In March 2020, the duo released their self-titled debut album, which includes their previously released singles.<ref name=van/> \n\n\"Set You Free\", which appears on their EP ''Midnight Sunshine'', is the theme song for the [[Netflix]] series ''Toy Boy''.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moreno |first1=Adriano |title=Los secretos que esconde 'Set You Free', la sensual sintonia de 'Toy Boy' |url=https://los40.com/los40/2019/09/25/musica/1569410777_628986.html |publisher=[[Los 40]]|language=Spanish|date=September 25, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n=== Studio albums ===\n* ''REYKO'' (2020)\n\n===EPs===\n*''Midnight Sunshine'' (2018)\n\n=== Singles ===\n* \"Spinning Over You\" (2017)\n* \"Lose Myself\" (2019) \n* \"Hierba Mala\" (2019) \n* \"Don't Mention my Name\" (2019)\n* \"Surrender\" (2020)\n* \"La Verdad\" (2020)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.reykomusic.com Official website]\n\n\n\n[[Category:Electropop groups]]\n", "name_user": "Bluevespa8", "label": "safe", "comment": "Minor edit adding information on History", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reyko"}
